    | object        | term          |
    | Brass lantern | lantern       |
    | Brass lantern | brass lantern |
    | Brass lantern | lamp          |
    | Brass lantern | brass lamp    |
    | Small bottle  | bottle        |
    | Small bottle  | water         |
    | Small bottle  | small bottle  |
    | Tasty food    | food          |

